   significant positive correlation was found between the BCOS score and
   MSPSS's family (r=0.31; p=0.007), friend (r=0.41; p<0.01) and special
   human (r=0.46; p<0.01) sub-parameters. In addition, there were
   significant positive correlations between BCOS score and the physical
